{
  "stem": "162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- I don't think, when I was in Germany during those times, I don't think I had an identity, except for the first time when I went to school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was registered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was in school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after that, I was just living with different people in different places in order not to be--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was-- I mean, I was constantly, constantly scared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I lived through the air raids in Berlin, some of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my grandparents lived in an apartment building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there were four stories or five stories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during the war, the elevators were not working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was an elevator, and then there were the spiral staircases all the way up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember, we lived on the top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during those air raids, I would always go to sleep with all my clothes on, with my shoes on, with my clothes on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember one time-- sometimes the sirens went off, and there wasn't time enough to get to the shelters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So one time I remember the sirens went off, and I tripped on the top stairwell, and I spiraled all the way down until I got to the next floor, but luckily, I wasn't hurt.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sometimes, because the shelter was not in our building, we had to walk outside about a half a block to the shelter in the next building.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sometimes you couldn't get out because the flak had started to fall from the bombs, and you could hear it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was like-- like huge stones falling on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then you had to wait until the flak stopped falling, and then you would run into the shelters.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
